bug.description: The purpose of this issue is to provide a test issue for the new label bot models that use repo specific models: see <denchmark-link:https://github.com/kubeflow/code-intelligence/issues/70>kubeflow/code-intelligence#70</denchmark-link> . So imagine we are trying to launch a notebook and we get exceptions complaining about the notebook not starting. This would be a problem.
